IMPORTANT NOTES ON DATASET USAGE:

This software is licensed under MIT License. However, if you use this software
with certain datasets for training or evaluation, you must comply with their
respective licenses:

1. FaceForensics++ Dataset:
   - License: Research and Educational Use Only
   - Commercial use is NOT permitted
   - Citation required (see README.md)
   - Access requires permission from the FaceForensics++ team
   - Website: http://kaldir.vc.in.tum.de/faceforensics/

2. Celeb-DF Dataset:
   - License: Research Use Only
   - Requires permission from dataset creators
   - Citation required

3. DFDC (DeepFake Detection Challenge) Dataset:
   - License: MIT License (compatible with this project)
   - Available via Kaggle

4. Pre-trained Models:
   - Any models you train on FaceForensics++ or Celeb-DF inherit the dataset's
     "Research Use Only" restriction
   - Commercial use of such models is NOT permitted
   - If you need commercial use, train your own model on commercially-licensed data

